data.description: Wonderful one level home in St. Helens with 4 bedrooms 2 bath on half Acre lot! Enjoy this home living in Town while enjoying nature. This home features beautiful finished white oak Hardwood floors, Master bedroom with bathroom and walk-in closet, oak kitchen cabinets, Hardwood floors under carpet in bedroom areas, gas fireplace, Central Heating & Central Air Conditioning. New deck, 2 Apple and 5 cherry trees, property includes 4 legal lots. Also, it may allow to build an ADU. Buyers to verify with local City and or County. great space to park RV, boat parking or working vehicles. Lots of room to build your own shop. Easy access to stores, School, restaurants, Columbia River boat ramps, Downtown St. Helens and HWY 30. Seller to provide a 1 YR home Warranty to buyers. This home is ready to move in!
